Enkarrueisho e tung'ana


1   Ore peyie eiteru iltung'ana aaponari tioriong enkop, netoikioki ninche intoyie, 
2  nedol ilayiok le Nkai intoyie oo ltung'ana ajo aisidain, neyaki ate inkituaak anaa enagelu tenena, anaa enayieu. 
3  Nejo Olaitoriani: “Meitoki enkiyanget ai amany tung'ani ntarasi, amu ore ninye naa osesen. Keaku inkolong'i enyena ilarin iip nabo o tikitam.” 
4   Etii sii apa Ilnefilim enkop te nena olong'i, ore peyie epuonu ilayiok le Nkai aajing'aki aayiolou intoyie oo ltung'ana, neiki ninche inkera. Naa kulo apa iltung'ana magil liopa laa aiyiolot oleng.


5   Nedol Olaitoriani enkarrueisho e tung'ani ajo etaa sapuk te nkop oleng, naa ore emusunoto endamunoto enye pooki e atua oltau naa entorroni ake eponaa. 
6  Neinosu Olaitoriani enkaraki naitobira oltung'ani te nkop, netum osina sapuk. 
7  Nejo Olaitoriani: “Kajutu tioriong enkop oltung'ani laitobira, tung'ani tenebo eng'ues, o pooki toki naiserpepiari, o motonyi o loing'ang'e, amu aanyaaka ainosu ajo ainyoo apa peyie aitobirua ninche.” 
8  Kake enoto Noa omom too nkonyek o Laitoriani.

Noa


9   Kuna ninche iishoritin e Noa. Ore apa Noa naa oltung'ani oitashe too sipat, nemeeta entioto to lporror lenye: eiriamariyie Noa Enkai. 
10  Eeta sii apa Noa ilayiok o kuni, Shem, o Ham o Yafet.


11  Etarruoyie apa enkop oleng too nkonyek e Enkai, neiputa ninye o larrabal. 
12  Nedol Enkai enkop ajo etarruoyie oleng. Amu ore iseseni pooki neitarruoitie inkoitoi enye te nkop. 
13  Nejoki Enkai Noa, “Atumuta to ltau ajo kaiting'ie pooki sesen, amu eiputa enkop o larrabal tenkaraki ninche, ng'ura kaidaikie nanu ninche o enkop.

Esafina


14  “Intaiki kewan esafina olchani le Gofer, nipik ilgilat atua esafina, nimur atua o oriong te nkoronko. 
15  Naa inji ayieu ninkunu. Ore enkadori e safina naa intemat e nkaina iip uni, ore elalai naa intemat e nkaina onom, ore enkilepata eiteru te kop naa intemat e nkaina tomoni uni. 
16  Ntushura sii esafina, ning'uaa erishata e ntemata nabo e nkaina, pee eyau ewang'an. Nipik sii kutuk aji e matua. Nipik atua iorot oo nkajijik e abori, e empolos, o neshumata. 
17  Amu ng'ura kayau olairrag loo nkariak shumata enkop, peyie eishu iseseni pooki oota enkiyang'et enkishui, napuku tiabori keper. Ore pooki toki natii enkop naa keye. 
18  Kake kaitasheyie olning'o lo sotua lai o iyie, naa aijing iyie e safina, iyie o layiok linono, o enkitok ino, o nkituaak oo layiok linono tenebo iyie. 
19  O pooki toki naishu e pooki sesen, iyau maare e pooki pukunoto atua e safina. Niramat ninche peyie meye; naa ore pooki naa oloing'oni ake o elipong. 
20  Enoo motonyi te risioroto oo mpukunot enye enoo ng'uesi te risioroto oo mpukunot enye, enoo naaiserpepiari te risioroto e mpukunoto enye. Ejing maare anaa impukunot enye enitii, peyie iramat meye. 
21  Ore sii, ayieu niya atua e safina indaiki oo mpukunot pooki tushuma. Naa keaku endaa ino o ninche.” 
22   Neas Noa ena; etaasa nena pooki naaitanapa Enkai ninye.

